.TH LIGHTNING-CHANNEL-UPTIME-KURTOSIS 1
.SH NAME
lightning-channel-uptime-kurtosis \- compute kurtosis of channel uptime distribution
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning channel-uptime-kurtosis
.SH DESCRIPTION
Queries listpeerchannels and computes the kurtosis of the uptime distribution across channels.
.SH OUTPUT
JSON object with field \fBuptime_kurtosis\fR.
